    "long_instructions": "### Free Play: Create Your Own Live Performance!\r\n\r\nNow it’s your turn to take everything you’ve learned and make it your own! In this level, you’ll explore, experiment, and build a live performance using loops, triggers, and effects..\r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/589b9aa091a4c02498a0a87f45d3d5aa-image-1742321504908.11.38 AM.png)\r\n\r\n**Do This**:\r\n- Set up your sound – Create a backtrack or start from scratch.\r\n- Use triggers – Add sounds, loops, or effects in real-time to shape your performance.\r\n- Create variations – Experiment with filters, timing, and layering to make your music dynamic.\r\n- Perform live! Play around, improvise, and see where the music takes you.\r\n\r\n",
